## A Quick Snippet

Since we're on the topic, here's a handy little TypeScript snippet I've recently learned:

```ts
async function getUserById(id: string): Promise<User> {
  const user = await db.findUserById(id)
  if (!user) {
    throw new Error("User not found")
  }
  return user
}
```

